## 3. STOP (The Manifestation)\par
In driving, stopping is about friction. In the XTP-1, "Stopping" is about **Frequency Braking** to allow the material to precipitate.\par
\par
* **The Action:** You engage the **Weft Coil** (the **Litz Wire** outer winding).\par
* **The Metric:** The **Golden Ratio (1.618) Harmonic**. If the Warp is 50 turns, the Weft must be 81 turns to act as the "Brake."\par
* **The Goal:** This creates the standing wave. You are "stopping" the transit of the particles exactly at the **Z-axis zero-datum** of the mandrel, forcing them to manifest as **99.9% pure Auric samples**.\par
* **Red Seal Check:** If the **Synthetic Quartz Resonator** drifts, the "brakes" fail. The material stays in a high-energy state and never hits the "Stop" (Solid-State) phase.\par
